Texts.Chs:
黑暗中的窃窃私语：暴言和恶德的惨烈吟唱。 恐惧随着骨头的嘎嘎声蔓延开来：脚步声。 他们知道那里有些东西，有些不对劲：他们可以听到。^gray;但是其在何处？^reset;

声音回荡，沿着巨大洞穴的崎岖的墙壁弹起。 每时每刻，吟唱声都在上升，这是疯狂的昏暗气氛。^gray;但，仍然看不见。^reset; 墙壁，天花板和地板散发出深黑色的雾气，就像细细的卷须在肺部扭曲，噎住了它们。、 当锯齿状的骨头像龙一样飞翔时，他们的战友落荒而逃，骨片穿过脖子，撕破皮肤。^red;血流成河。

^gray;但是，仍不见影。^reset;

And then the whispers stop, as if they had never started, and the smoke dissipates, ^red;and only bones remain.

Texts.Eng:
Whispers in the dark: a greusome chant of violent words and malicious thought. Fear creeps in as bones rattle: footsteps. They know something is there, that something is amiss: they can hear it. ^gray;But where?^reset;

The sounds echo, bouncing along the rocky, rugged walls of a massive cavern. With every passing moment, the chants crescendo, a cacophany of madness. ^gray;But still, nothing in sight.^reset; A dark, black mist emanates from the walls and from the ceiling and from the floor, like wispy tendrils twisting at their lungs, choking them. All around their comrades drop, as jagged bones like dragons fly, slicing through necks and tearing through skin. ^red;Blood pools.

^gray;But still, nothing.^reset;

And then the whispers stop, as if they had never started, and the smoke dissipates, ^red;and only bones remain.

Texts.Chs:
在螺旋的黑暗中，一滴光明依然存在。
^magenta;把它闷死。^reset;
随着光线渐渐暗淡，烧焦的余烬迸发出火花，划去了历史的线条。 时间不是绝对的: 不，当然不是。
^magenta;但你就是。^reset;
厌恶。 恐惧。恐怖。仇恨。忽略他们。不要理会他们的注视和颤抖。忽略它们。因为他们不明白: 不管他们的呼喊、恳求和希望，你们都会扼杀他们的生命，取而代之。毕竟:
^magenta;死亡面前人人平等...

Texts.Eng:
Within the swirling darkness, a single drop of light remains.

^magenta;Smother it.^reset;

As the light fades, blackened embers spark, crossing out lines in history. Time is not absolute: no, of course not.

^magenta;But you are.^reset;

Disgust. Fear. Horror. Hatred. Ignore them. Ignore the stares and shudders. Ignore them all. For they do not understand: despite their cries, pleas, and hopes; you will snuff their life and replace it. After all:

^magenta;Death comes for us all...
